<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Dashboard Concierge - Julho 2026</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>

*{
  box-sizing:border-box;
  margin:0;
  padding:0;
}

body{
  font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;
  background:#e5e7eb;
  min-height:100vh;
  display:flex;
  justify-content:center;
  align-items:center;
  padding:0;
}

.dashboard-container{
  width:1600px;
  height:900px;
  background:#f8fafc;
  padding:20px 30px;
  border-radius:12px;
  box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);

  display:flex;
  flex-direction:column;
  gap:15px;
  overflow:hidden;
}

/* HEADER */

.top-header{
  background:linear-gradient(90deg,#001a99 0%,#0052cc 100%);
  color:white;
  padding:10px 25px;
  display:flex;
  justify-content:space-between;
  align-items:center;
  border-radius:8px;
}

.title{
  font-size:20px;
  font-weight:700;
}

.slide-info{
  font-size:11px;
  font-weight:600;
  letter-spacing:1px;
  color:#93c5fd;
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  gap:8px;
}

.slide-info .date{
  color:#fff;
  font-size:20px;
  font-weight:800;
}

/* KPI */

.kpis-wrapper{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:1fr;
}

.kpi-group{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:repeat(6,1fr);
  gap:10px;

  background:#fff;
  border-radius:8px;
  padding:10px;
  border-left:4px solid #0026d9;
}

.kpi-card{
  background:#f8fafc;
  border:1px solid #e2e8f0;
  border-radius:6px;
  padding:12px 6px;
  text-align:center;
}

.kpi-value{
  font-size:24px;
  font-weight:800;
  margin-bottom:5px;
}

.kpi-label{
  font-size:10px;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  color:#64748b;
  font-weight:700;
}

.kpi-delta{
  margin-top:6px;
  font-size:11px;
  font-weight:800;
}

.delta-up{
  color:#16a34a;
}

.delta-down{
  color:#ef4444;
}

/* SPLIT */

.split-layout{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
  gap:20px;
  flex:1;
}

.side-panel{
  background:#fff;
  border-radius:10px;
  border:1px solid #e2e8f0;
  padding:15px 20px;
  display:flex;
  flex-direction:column;
}

.panel-header{
  display:flex;
  justify-content:space-between;
  align-items:center;
  border-bottom:2px solid #0026d9;
  padding-bottom:8px;
  margin-bottom:12px;
}

.panel-title{
  font-size:18px;
  font-weight:900;
  color:#0026d9;
}

.launch-badge{
  background:#eff6ff;
  color:#0026d9;
  font-size:10px;
  font-weight:700;
  padding:4px 8px;
  border-radius:4px;
}

.rankings-wrapper{
  display:flex;
  flex-direction:column;
  gap:15px;
}

.ranking-section{
  display:flex;
  flex-direction:column;
}

.ranking-title{
  font-size:12px;
  font-weight:800;
  color:#334155;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  margin-bottom:6px;
}

.list-header{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:24px 1fr 50px;
  gap:10px;
  font-size:9px;
  color:#64748b;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  font-weight:800;
  margin-bottom:8px;
}

.list-header-dual{
  grid-template-columns:24px 1fr 65px 50px;
}

.ranking-list{
  display:flex;
  flex-direction:column;
  gap:8px;
}

.ranking-item{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:24px 1fr 50px;
  gap:10px;
  align-items:center;
}

.ranking-item-dual{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:24px 1fr 65px 50px;
  gap:10px;
  align-items:center;
}

.rank-num{
  width:24px;
  height:24px;
  border-radius:4px;
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  justify-content:center;
  background:#0026d9;
  color:#fff;
  font-size:11px;
  font-weight:800;
}

.item-name{
  font-size:13px;
  font-weight:700;
  color:#1e293b;
}

.item-pct{
  font-size:13px;
  font-weight:800;
  text-align:right;
}

.item-pct-red{
  color:#ef4444;
  font-size:13px;
  font-weight:800;
  text-align:right;
}

.bar-bg{
  grid-column:2/span 2;
  width:100%;
  height:4px;
  background:#f1f5f9;
  border-radius:2px;
}

.ranking-item-dual .bar-bg{
  grid-column:2/span 3;
}

.bar-fill{
  height:100%;
  border-radius:2px;
  background:#3b82f6;
}

/* CARDS EXECUTIVOS */

.exec-card{
  border-radius:8px;
  padding:18px;
}

.exec-big{
  font-size:34px;
  font-weight:900;
  margin-bottom:8px;
  line-height:1;
}

.exec-text{
  font-size:14px;
  line-height:1.5;
  color:#334155;
}

/* DEEP DIVE */

.deep-dive-panel{
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f172a 0%,#1e1b4b 100%);
  border-radius:12px;
  padding:15px 25px;
  color:white;
  border-left:6px solid #34d399;
}

.dd-header{
  display:flex;
  justify-content:space-between;
  align-items:center;
  gap:15px;
  padding-bottom:8px;
  margin-bottom:10px;
  border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
}

.dd-title{
  font-size:16px;
  font-weight:800;
  color:#34d399;
}

.dd-badge{
  background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  padding:6px 12px;
  border-radius:12px;
  font-size:11px;
  font-weight:700;
  white-space:nowrap;
}

.dd-body{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:1fr 1.8fr;
  gap:30px;
}

.flow-container{
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  justify-content:space-between;
  background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  padding:15px;
  border-radius:8px;
}

.flow-box{
  text-align:center;
}

.flow-box-title{
  font-size:10px;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  color:#94a3b8;
  font-weight:700;
  margin-bottom:4px;
}

.flow-box-value{
  font-size:18px;
  font-weight:800;
}

.flow-box-value b{
  display:block;
  color:#ef4444;
  font-size:28px;
}

.flow-arrow{
  color:#34d399;
  font-size:28px;
  font-weight:900;
}

.qualitative-container{
  display:flex;
  flex-direction:column;
  gap:10px;
}

.qualitative-text{
  font-size:14px;
  line-height:1.5;
  color:#e2e8f0;
}

.qualitative-box{
  background:rgba(239,68,68,0.1);
  border-left:4px solid #ef4444;
  padding:12px 15px;
  border-radius:6px;
}

.qualitative-title{
  font-size:11px;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  color:#fca5a5;
  font-weight:800;
  margin-bottom:8px;
}

.qualitative-list{
  list-style:none;
  display:flex;
  flex-direction:column;
  gap:5px;
}

.qualitative-list li{
  font-size:13px;
  font-weight:600;
  color:#fff;
  display:flex;
  align-items:flex-start;
  gap:6px;
  line-height:1.4;
}

.qualitative-list li::before{
  content:'✕';
  color:#ef4444;
  font-weight:900;
}

.dd-footer{
  margin-top:10px;
  font-size:10px;
  color:#94a3b8;
  text-align:right;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="dashboard-container">

  <!-- HEADER -->
  <div class="top-header">

    <div class="title">
      Comitê CX — Concierge | Evolução Operacional
    </div>

    <div class="slide-info">
      RESULTADOS
      <span class="date">JUL/26</span>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- KPI -->
  <div class="kpis-wrapper">

    <div class="kpi-group">

      <div class="kpi-card">
        <div class="kpi-value">2.184</div>
        <div class="kpi-label">Vol. Ofer.</div>
        <div class="kpi-delta delta-down">▼ -26,1% vs Jun</div>
      </div>

      <div class="kpi-card">
        <div class="kpi-value">92,27%</div>
        <div class="kpi-label">NS</div>
        <div class="kpi-delta delta-up">▲ +2,99 p.p</div>
      </div>

      <div class="kpi-card">
        <div class="kpi-value">1.403s</div>
        <div class="kpi-label">TMO</div>
        <div class="kpi-delta delta-down">▲ +66s</div>
      </div>

      <div class="kpi-card">
        <div class="kpi-value">64,21%</div>
        <div class="kpi-label">Resolutiv.</div>
        <div class="kpi-delta delta-up">▲ +18,6 p.p</div>
      </div>

      <div class="kpi-card">
        <div class="kpi-value">66,53%</div>
        <div class="kpi-label">CSAT</div>
        <div class="kpi-delta delta-up">▲ +11,9 p.p</div>
      </div>

      <div class="kpi-card">
        <div class="kpi-value" style="color:#16a34a;">4,53%</div>
        <div class="kpi-label">Rechamada</div>
        <div class="kpi-delta delta-up">▼ -5,77 p.p</div>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- SPLIT -->
  <div class="split-layout">

    <!-- ESQUERDA -->
    <div class="side-panel">

      <div class="panel-header">
        <div class="panel-title">🛎️ CONCIERGE</div>
        <div class="launch-badge">Julho/26</div>
      </div>

      <div class="rankings-wrapper">

        <div class="ranking-section">

          <div class="ranking-title">
            📞 TOP MOTIVOS DE CHAMADA
          </div>

          <div class="list-header">
            <div></div>
            <div>Motivo</div>
            <div style="text-align:right;">Repres.</div>
          </div>

          <div class="ranking-list">

            <div class="ranking-item">
              <div class="rank-num">1</div>
              <div class="item-name">Ressarcimento</div>
              <div class="item-pct">21%</div>

              <div class="bar-bg">
                <div class="bar-fill" style="width:100%;"></div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="ranking-item">
              <div class="rank-num">2</div>
              <div class="item-name">Valores debitados</div>
              <div class="item-pct">15%</div>

              <div class="bar-bg">
                <div class="bar-fill" style="width:71%;"></div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="ranking-item">
              <div class="rank-num">3</div>
              <div class="item-name">Dúvidas Contratação</div>
              <div class="item-pct">6%</div>

              <div class="bar-bg">
                <div class="bar-fill" style="width:28%;"></div>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>

        </div>

        <div class="ranking-section">

          <div class="ranking-title">
            🔄 TOP MOTIVOS DE RECHAMADA
          </div>

          <div class="list-header list-header-dual">
            <div></div>
            <div>Motivo</div>
            <div style="text-align:right;color:#ef4444;">% Rech.</div>
            <div style="text-align:right;">Repres.</div>
          </div>

          <div class="ranking-list">

            <div class="ranking-item-dual">

              <div class="rank-num" style="background:#ef4444;">1</div>
              <div class="item-name">Ressarcimento</div>
              <div class="item-pct-red">21%</div>
              <div class="item-pct">29%</div>

              <div class="bar-bg">
                <div class="bar-fill" style="background:#ef4444;width:100%;"></div>
              </div>

            </div>

            <div class="ranking-item-dual">

              <div class="rank-num" style="background:#f97316;">2</div>
              <div class="item-name">Transação Não Autorizada</div>
              <div class="item-pct-red">100%</div>
              <div class="item-pct">14%</div>

              <div class="bar-bg">
                <div class="bar-fill" style="background:#f97316;width:48%;"></div>
              </div>

            </div>

            <div class="ranking-item-dual">

              <div class="rank-num" style="background:#eab308;">3</div>
              <div class="item-name">PIX</div>
              <div class="item-pct-red">14%</div>
              <div class="item-pct">14%</div>

              <div class="bar-bg">
                <div class="bar-fill" style="background:#eab308;width:48%;"></div>
              </div>

            </div>

          </div>

        </div>

      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- DIREITA -->
    <div class="side-panel">

      <div class="panel-header">
        <div class="panel-title">
          📈 EVOLUÇÃO JULHO vs JUNHO
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rankings-wrapper">

        <div class="exec-card" style="background:#f0fdf4;border-left:5px solid #16a34a;">

          <div class="exec-big" style="color:#16a34a;">
            +18,6 p.p
          </div>

          <div class="exec-text">
            Resolutividade saiu de
            <b>45,61%</b>
            para
            <b>64,21%</b>.
          </div>

        </div>

        <div class="exec-card" style="background:#eff6ff;border-left:5px solid #2563eb;">

          <div class="exec-big" style="color:#2563eb;">
            +11,9 p.p
          </div>

          <div class="exec-text">
            CSAT evoluiu de
            <b>54,61%</b>
            para
            <b>66,53%</b>.
          </div>

        </div>

        <div class="exec-card" style="background:#fef2f2;border-left:5px solid #ef4444;">

          <div class="exec-big" style="color:#ef4444;">
            -56%
          </div>

          <div class="exec-text">
            Rechamada caiu de
            <b>10,3%</b>
            para
            <b>4,53%</b>.
          </div>

        </div>

        <div class="exec-card" style="background:#fff7ed;border-left:5px solid #f97316;">

          <div class="exec-big" style="color:#f97316;">
            +66s
          </div>

          <div class="exec-text">
            TMO aumentou de
            <b>1.337s</b>
            para
            <b>1.403s</b>.
          </div>

        </div>

      </div>

    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- DEEP DIVE -->
  <div class="deep-dive-panel">

    <div class="dd-header">

      <div class="dd-title">
        📉 DEEP DIVE CONCIERGE
      </div>

      <div class="dd-badge">
        Rechamada caiu de <b>10,3%</b> para <b>4,53%</b>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="dd-body">

      <div class="flow-container">

        <div class="flow-box">
          <div class="flow-box-title">Maior Ofensor</div>

          <div class="flow-box-value">
            Ressarcimento
            <br>
            <b>21%</b>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flow-arrow">→</div>

        <div class="flow-box">
          <div class="flow-box-title">Impacto em Rechamada</div>

          <div class="flow-box-value">
            Reincidência
            <br>
            <b>29%</b>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="qualitative-container">

        <p class="qualitative-text">
          Julho apresentou melhora expressiva nos principais indicadores operacionais,
          demonstrando evolução de experiência e capacidade de resolução.
          Apesar da melhora, Ressarcimento segue como principal driver de contatos reincidentes.
        </p>

        <div class="qualitative-box">

          <div class="qualitative-title">
            Fricções Qualitativas
          </div>

          <ul class="qualitative-list">
            <li>Baixa autonomia do cliente para acompanhar status.</li>
            <li>Prazo percebido elevado para devolução financeira.</li>
            <li>Dependência excessiva de atendimento humano.</li>
          </ul>

        </div>

      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="dd-footer">
      Fonte: Comparativo Operacional Concierge — Junho vs Julho/26
    </div>

  </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
